name: aspartate-semialdehyde dehydrogenase
classes: Acting on the aldehyde or oxo group of donors;
With NAD+ or NADP+ as acceptor
reaction: L-aspartate 4-semialdehyde + phosphate + NADP+ = L-4-aspartyl phosphate + NADPH + H+ [RN:R02291]

Aldehyde dehydrogenases.
